Realia May Buy Bankia’s KIO Tower in Madrid, Cinco Dias Reports

-- B y   C h a r l e s   P e n t y
-- 
2011-05-31T06:04:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/realia-may-buy-bankia-s-kio-tower-in-madrid-cinco-dias-reports.html
Realia Business SA (RLIA)  may be interested
in buying the KIO Tower in  Madrid  from Bankia, Cinco Dias
reported.  Caja Madrid , the savings bank at the head of Bankia, has
hired Aguirre Newman to find a buyer for the tower, which houses
its head office, the newspaper said. Realia sees the purchase as
an “interesting” option, the newspaper said, without saying
where it got the information.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
